<note n="0819022" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0819022">猗＝倚【三】</note>
<note n="0819023" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0819023">安息…藏＝沙門【三】</note>
<note n="0819024" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0819024">亦＝本【三】</note>
<note n="0819025" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0819025">有從致＝從癡有【三】</note>
<note n="0820001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820001">信＋（故）【三】</note>
